            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Use Google search operators: "resources" + your topic, "useful links" + your topic, "inurl:resources" + your topic. Ahrefs Content Explorer can also find pages with "resources" in their title that already link to competitors.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
