            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Personalised resource page outreach targeting relevant pages typically sees 5-15% response rates, with 2-8% resulting in a live link. These rates significantly outperform generic link outreach because the ask is clearly beneficial to the page owner.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

